docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files.

docs.text: Who I Am I'm a passionate Computer Science student at University of Technology, specializing in web development and UI/UX design. I love turning complex problems into simple, beautiful, and intuitive digital experiences. With a background in design and a passion for technology, I bridge the gap between aesthetics and functionality. I'm currently exploring machine learning applications in creative fields and building projects that make a difference. When I'm not coding, you can find me hiking, photography, or exploring new coffee shops around the city. Technical Skills HTML5 & CSS3 JavaScript React Node.js Python UI/UX Design Figma Git & GitHub
